Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The three Musais led by Lieutenant Dren\Nwaited in the White Base's path...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...but were eliminated by the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base then set\Na course for Side 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell in Side Six
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.03,0:01:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This region was once the site of Side 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:02:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it is the location of Solomon,\Nheadquarters of the Space Attack Force...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...commanded by Vice Admiral Dozle Zabi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Conscon Mobile Unit\Nis about to be deployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Dozle was displeased that\Nhis sister Kycilia was using Char's services.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He wished he could personally destroy the\NTrojan Horse and prove Char's incompetence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.39,0:02:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...until he discovered the objectives\Nof the Tianem Fleet assembling at Luna II...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...he could not afford to send out\Nany more military power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Ms. Sayla?\NNothing unusual, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:03:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, everything seems to be normal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are so many rocks here,\Nit's hard to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai! Do you read? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No problems! But I've got low\Nfuel reserves, so I'm heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like us to patrol a bit longer\Nin the G-Armor. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll give me a chance to learn more\Nabout the navigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Amuro.\NHow do you feel about Fraw Bow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? Because you've beentely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Friendships are important in times like these.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I hate her or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.94,0:03:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Portside!\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They've spotted us.\NWe should attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold off a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They had to come during a malfunction!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are the engines working?\N- Somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Oh no! Ms. Sayla, get back!\N- What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They're firing at us!\NIt's a Zeon mobile armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure it's a mobile armor...\NHere it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! Why did you shoot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They were coming to attack us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what they intended! Careless fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This mobile armor's unusual!\NLet's go behind the rock so we can bolt out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- I've overpowered the engine!\N- Never mind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy has seen our Braw-Bro,\Nso we must destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,3... 2... 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one enemy... Let's finish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The attacks are coming from odd angles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are those shots coming from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's their fastest speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And we were so close\Nto deploying it in combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That took some time, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We should return to the White Base\Nbefore it enters Side 6 airspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Within these beacons\Nlies Side 6 airspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, the forces of both\NZeon and the Earth Federation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...are prohibited from all warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Cameron Bloom,\NSide 6 Prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We've sealed all the White Base's\Nmissile launchers, guns, and beam cannons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If even one of them is broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do understand.\NIf that happened, we'd pay a very stiff fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you about our ship's repairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to do that within Side 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be considered assisting the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to take you to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That attack definitely came from somewhere\Nother than the mobile armor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't just seeing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Amuro must have encountered\Nsome new mobile armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Perfect timing. We're about to enter port.\N- Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Approach angle good.\NEntry speed 05.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Entering Side 6's Palda Bay!\NAll hands, prepare for docking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser sensors open 360 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mirai! It's you, Mirai!\N- Cameron! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai! You made it through alive! M-Mirai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Who is that?\N- A relative?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Cameron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the middle of docking.\NPlease restrain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Ensign Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Right... Beg your pardon, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy. I'd given up all hope\Nof ever seeing you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this war broke out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If your father hadn't passed away,\Nwe might've avoided the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I might not have\Nhad to emigrate to Side 7 either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just it.\NWhy didn't you let me know, Mirai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was desperate to find out where you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Desperate...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I had people look for you everywhere.\NYou wouldn't believe how much I spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So why didn't you look\Nfor me yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was busy emigrating here\Nto Side 6 around that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Our engagement was merely to please\Nour parents, wasn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true, Mirai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong.\NWon't you come home with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Father will be so thrilled!\N- What? But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't regret it.\NMirai, I'd do anything for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow down a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate seeing a guy harassing a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Sleggar, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you sure?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard the lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Fancypants! Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Have your glasses back.\N- Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Cameron. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:10:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It seems I don't know how\Nto court a lady properly. Right, Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, Ensign Mirai's like a mother\Nto all of us on the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,One moment you're serving\Nunder Vice Admiral Dozle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the next, you serve\Nunder Rear Admiral Kycilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you ashamed of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times have you allowed\Nthe Trojan Horse to escape? Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I show you how it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch and learn something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who told you that you were dismissed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't bully your juniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll happily observe you in action, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't he ever remove that mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Allegedly it's a terrible burn...\NBut some rumors say he's quite handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll strip that wolf of his sheepskin one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the Rick Dom team\Nthat infiltrated around Palda Bay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! As of yet, they haven't been discovered,\Neven by Side 6's patrol ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mulligan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Send an encrypted message\Nto Rear Admiral Kycilia from the Zanzibar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sir!\N- "Pararom Zu, Char." Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask any questions.\NIt's classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tamura. Did you exchange your money?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The center of this artificial space-city...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...is a zero-gravity zone,\Nwhere one experiences weightlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,From here, an elevator descends\Nover 3000 meters...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...to artificial ground\Nwhere one can feel one's own weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mountains, forests, and rivers\Nhave been formed there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...to create a landscape\Nmuch like that of Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, a modern city has also been built.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wow! This is great!\N- This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, I can change up the menu a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Father...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna check out that bookstore there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... it's you, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So how's the Gundam faring in battle?\NIs it doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?! Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about junkyards is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...they're ideal for intelligence gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been living here lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to install this\Nin the Gundam's memory circuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I developed it based on the circuits\Nfrom Zeon mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's practically an antique!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's suffering from oxygen deficiency.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing. It'll increase the Gundam's\Ncombat abilities several times over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.39,0:14:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Install this and test it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I will. But what about you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of research to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in touch again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...\NI saw Mom back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you concerned about how Mom is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Yes. The war will be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it's finished, let's visit the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Get going! You're a soldier now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro. I don't recall giving you permission\Nto wander around the city on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Our departure's been delayed, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, sir.g so suddenly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Escort the White Base out in the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mr. Bergamino.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure that's what\NProsecutor Cameron Bloom requested?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I got a video call from the Prime\NMinister's residence. There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If the dock's located outside the airspace...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...we're permitted to repair any vessel,\Nwhether Zeon or Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're being pursued. Will it really be safe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have connections\Nwith the top brass on both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Young lady, you have no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Bergamino.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yo, Amuro. You feeling okay now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Always was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that so? Glad to hear It. That's a good boy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Mr. Sleggar.\N- What Is It?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please\Nput a lid on that "good boy" stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sure. Sorry 'bout that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Looks like the Trojan Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How kind of them to come out on their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the floating dock?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A signal flare from Kayahawa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That means the Trojan Horse\Nhas left Side 6 airspace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirm its position!\NEngines to maximum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did the Trojan Horse leave so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Position confirmed!\NThey're at Bergamino's floating dock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bergamino?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That war profiteer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is directly\Nin our fleet's line of fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch 12 Rick Doms!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Conscon has detected the Trojan Horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They've launched their Rick Doms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:17:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Is this a trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Not my precious dock!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright! Cameron isn't\Nthe kind of person who'd do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All units, hurry up and launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Lieutenant! Please keep your ship\Naway from my dock!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then my precious dock will be saved!\N- We're doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The suits with skirts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,One down! Next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Target the ship in the center! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy managed to destroy the Kwamel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Doms?!\NHow are the Rick Doms doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let up on your attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that where Bergamino's\Nfloating dock is located?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How did the Zeons find out?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We must stop them from fighting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let any of their stray beams\Nenter Side 6 airspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them were destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All 12 Rick Doms were destroyed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wiped out in under 3 minutes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost 12 Rick Doms\Nto one badly damaged warship...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's some kind of monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Zanzibar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Char! Has he come to laugh at me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- The Zanzibar's approaching!\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright! Let's retreat to Side 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Order all machines to retreat\Nto Side 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about my dock...\NMy precious dock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't attack!\NThat's a Side 6 patrol ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Conscon's group to stop firing as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitting a patrol ship would start\Nan international incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Cameron!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking extra risks to stop a battle\Nisn't in my job description!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But my future wife happens to be\Naboard that Federation Forces ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Father will cover up the fact\Nthat you broke the weapon seals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:22:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... with Father's help\NI can arrange for you to live here in Side 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,0:22:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm supposed to abandon the White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.91,0:22:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...what are you willing to do for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I've been saying...\NI'll ask Father to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't understand anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.97,0:22:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...\NI can't abandon the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.12,0:22:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You would never have said\Nsomething like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.73,0:22:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.60,0:22:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for the war...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know... That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Cameron. You've done nothing but\Nescape from the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you! That's something\NI could never change, Mirai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... That means a lot to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.31,0:22:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mirai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.13,0:22:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that you don't like about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.36,0:22:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.47,0:23:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to change, if that's what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.36,0:23:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A young girl, Lalah, predicts that\NAmuro and Char will meet face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Far from the battlefield,\Nthe seeds of the next battle are sprouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bearing many different destinies...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...the White Base launches into space\Nwhere the enemy awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.84,0:23:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NA Fateful Encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A Fateful Encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.68,0:23:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:54.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:09.75,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:14.68,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.31,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:24.69,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:39.58,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:54.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:09.75,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:14.68,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.31,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:24.69,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:39.58,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
